# Republic (Opendeal Inc.)

**Last Updated:** 2026-03-07

## Company Overview
- **Sector:** Blockchain, Crowdfunding, Secondary Markets
- **Status:** Active, targeting ~B secondary exit

## Recent Developments (2025-2026)

### Major Transaction: INX Digital Acquisition (Nov 2025)
- Republic (OpenDeal Inc.) successfully completed plan of arrangement with INX Digital Company
- INX Digital acquired via subsidiary structure
- Transaction closed November 10, 2025
- Source: [Crowdfund Insider](https://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2025/11/255476-the-inx-digital-co-announces-closing-of-transaction-with-republic/)

### Product Offerings
- **Integrated Launchpad:** Blockchain + self-custody wallet integration
- **RWA Tokenization:** Complete marketplace for real-world-assets and tokenized securities
  - Tokenization services
  - Offering hosting
  - Token management
- Platform connecting blockchain protocols with Republic's crowdfunding infrastructure

### Corporate Status
- Operating as OpenDeal Inc. d/b/a Republic
- Not a registered broker-dealer (operates under different regulatory framework)

## Strategic Direction
- Expanding blockchain + traditional finance integration
- RWA tokenization focus
- Secondary market development for private securities
- Hiring actively

